<div class="emailbody">
<!--TEMPLATE FlatDetailAgenda.chtml-->
<h1>Welcome to Weaver!</h1> 

<p>Your site 
{% loop in $site.names as $name %}
'<b>{$name}</b>'
{% endloop %}
 is up and running</p>

<p>As a new Weaver site owner we suggest that you visit the 
<a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL-y45TQ2Eb40eQWwH5NjyIjgepk_MonlB">Weaver training channel</a> 
and review the training video 
<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sSJPN5XRFsY&list=PL-y45TQ2Eb40eQWwH5NjyIjgepk_MonlB&t=38s&index=2">Weaver for First Time User</a> 
and the video 
<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sSJPN5XRFsY&list=PL-y45TQ2Eb40eQWwH5NjyIjgepk_MonlB&t=38s&index=2">Adding Users to Weaver.</a> 
</p>


<p>You can access the site at any time using one of the following links.   We recommend you bookmark one of these links right away:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="{$baseUrl}v/{$site.key}/$/SiteWorkspaces.htm">Workspaces</a> - a list of all workspaces in the site</li>
<li><a href="{$baseUrl}v/{$site.key}/$/SiteAdmin.htm">Site Admin</a> - the configuration options for the owner (you)</li>
<li><a href="{$baseUrl}v/{$site.key}/$/roleManagement.htm">Roles</a> - the roles (user groups) for the entire site</li>
</ul>

<p>Go ahead and create a workspace if you have not already!</p>
</div>
